%% High-level pipeline: Quantum Systemic Stress Scenario Discovery
```mermaid
flowchart LR
  subgraph Input[Input]
    Spec[[SystemSpec / NetworkSpec]]
  end

  Spec -->|marginals, correlations, exposures| Generators[Scenario Generators]

  subgraph GeneratorsGroup[Generators]
    Classical[Classical\n(Bernoulli / Copula / Ising)]
    Entangled[Entangled / Quantum\n(Born-machine / PQC)]
    Layout[Clustering / Entanglement Layout]
  end

  Generators --> Classical
  Generators --> Entangled
  Spec --> Layout
  Layout --> Entangled

  Classical --> Simulator[Contagion Simulator\n(deterministic, generator-agnostic)]
  Entangled --> Simulator

  Simulator --> Metrics[Metrics\n(loss, rounds, CVaR, tail probs)]
  Metrics --> Evaluation[Evaluation Harness & Comparison]
  Evaluation --> Visuals[Visualisation & Reports]
  Evaluation --> Tests[Automated tests]
```
